{"analytics_identifier":"OT1116","base_path":"/government/organisations/government-commercial-function","content_id":"ddbddda2-2460-4ed5-a274-d6731376bef8","description":"The Government Commercial Function is a cross-government network procuring or supporting the procurement of goods and services for the government. GCF is part of the Civil Service and the Cabinet Office .","details":{"acronym":"GCF","alternative_format_contact_email":"publiccorrespondence@cabinetoffice.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Government Commercial Function is a cross-government network procuring or supporting the procurement of goods and services for the government.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Government Commercial Function\">GCF</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/civil-service\">Civil Service</a> and the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"cabinet-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Government Commercial Function"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"About","href":"/government/organisations/government-commercial-function/about","image":{"alt_text":"whitehall","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a51bf84e5274a6bf0561f44/s712_whitehall_960_640.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a51bf80e5274a6bf0561f42/s465_whitehall_960_640.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a51bf7e40f0b648ca1e6201/whitehall_960_640.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-03-06T10:36:47.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Government Commercial Function is a cross-government network procuring or supporting the procurement of goods and services for the government.</p>\n</div>","title":"About us"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/the-sourcing-and-consultancy-playbooks","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60a686fde90e071b5f4d5562/s712_Cabinet_office_facade.JPG","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60a686fdd3bf7f737bdd14fb/s465_Cabinet_office_facade.JPG","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60a686fdd3bf7f73893a8e26/Cabinet_office_facade.JPG"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-30T15:13:55.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Key policies and guidance for making sourcing decisions for the delivery of public services</p>\n</div>","title":"The Sourcing Playbook"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/the-construction-playbook","image":{"alt_text":"Abstract image","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60462799d3bf7f1d0da756e9/s712_logo.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/604627998fa8f577bf0744bf/s465_logo.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60462799e90e077ddcbbc621/logo.png"},"public_updated_at":"2023-07-11T14:19:23.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Construction Playbook sets out key policies and guidance for how public works projects and programmes are assessed, procured and delivered.</p>\n</div>","title":"The Construction Playbook"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/civil-service-helping-you-with-managing-suppliers-and-contracts","image":{"alt_text":"Helping you with managing suppliers and contracts in government","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5ad4b361ed915d32a65dbbb2/s712_contract-manager-header-image-govuk.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5ad4b33440f0b617df335aa6/s465_contract-manager-header-image-govuk.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5ad4b333ed915d32a65dbbb0/contract-manager-header-image-govuk.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-01-20T13:37:23.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Information on new training and accreditation available for any civil servant who works with contracts or suppliers, even if this is a small part of your role.</p>\n</div>","title":"Civil Service: helping you with managing contracts and suppliers"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/government-commercial-organisation","image":{"alt_text":"Government Commercial Organisation","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5b169ee6ed915d2cb4e19114/s712_Shapes-66.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5b169ee6e5274a1912717883/s465_Shapes-66.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5b169ee640f0b634c24e61fc/Shapes-66.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-13T12:04:31.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>An overview of the Government Commercial Organisation (GCO) and where it sits with the Government Commercial Function (GCF).</p>\n</div>","title":"Government Commercial Organisation"},{"document_type":"Policy paper","href":"/government/publications/government-commercial-function-people-standards-for-the-profession","image":{"alt_text":"People Standards for the Commercial Profession in Government","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5ad897fee5274a76be66c6ca/s712_Shapes-44.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5ad8981bed915d32a65dbed8/s465_Shapes-44.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5ad897feed915d32a3a70e82/Shapes-44.png"},"public_updated_at":"2021-05-10T09:41:59.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This document sets out the standards expected from commercial professionals in government. It will help you with recruitment or career development.</p>\n</div>","title":"People standards for the commercial profession"}],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"sub_organisation","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2015-03-20T14:41:02+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1116","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/government-commercial-function","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/government-commercial-function","base_path":"/government/organisations/government-commercial-function","content_id":"ddbddda2-2460-4ed5-a274-d6731376bef8","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-04-15T09:03:57Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Government Commercial Function","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-commercial-function","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/andrew-forzani","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/andrew-forzani","base_path":"/government/people/andrew-forzani","content_id":"2248ccef-fec2-4f08-bad3-2b2b57ecb3e8","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Andrew Forzani","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61bb53c0d3bf7f054e76960b/s465_20211216-ForzaniA_960x640.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"ec1aac85-1294-4a53-90d7-a1c400ad4837","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":3,"started_on":"2026-04-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"df8a5ee7-bb09-4d05-b689-6f0ecc01bf05","details":{"body":"<p>The Chair is responsible for  setting the strategic direction and aims of GCA, and supporting the CEO in making decisions that enable the organisation to achieve those aims.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-01T10:44:20Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Chair, Government Commercial Agency","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-01T10:44:44Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Andrew Forzani - Non-Executive Chair, Government Commercial Agency","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"2f5d817c-5b3c-458f-9a4b-71f9ca6bcbd1","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2025-02-24T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"8461ba35-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>Reporting to the Chief Executive of the Civil Service, the Government Chief Commercial Officer shapes and leads the programme of commercial reform across government.</p>\n\n<p>The Government Chief Commercial Officer’s priorities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Leading the Government Commercial Function and Governments Grants Management Functions (GCF and GGMF)</li>\n  <li>To steer the cross-government commercial and grants communities in delivering the Plan for Change</li>\n  <li>Delivering efficiencies and savings through the use of digital, data and AI</li>\n  <li>Lead the Functional Strategy</li>\n  <li>Leads the relationship with HMG Strategic Suppliers</li>\n  <li>Improving contract delivery and contract management</li>\n  <li>Advancing the capability of the GCF and GGMF</li>\n  <li>Head of Profession, building a commercial and grants community across the UK</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The Government Chief Commercial Officer works closely with departmental ministers, the Cabinet Secretary, departmental permanent secretaries and other senior officials, and senior leaders of government suppliers. The Government Chief Commercial Officer gives evidence to Parliamentary Select Committees, including the Public Accounts Committee, on commercial matters.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","pub